title: UNDERDOG MENTALITY
itunes:title: UNDERDOG MENTALITY
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
This is for all those who have been THE UNDERDOG most of their lives. Let them doubt you, let them talk down to you, let them laugh. The best fuel in the world is having the UNDERDOG MENTALITY! One of the BEST Motivational Speeches EVER featuring Marcus A Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity).


Music by Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube).
